Weighted Assessments. O Levels. A Levels. Uni applications. Career planning.\
\
Singapore teaches us to have a plan for everything.\
\
But nobody gave us a roadmap for the deeper questions… Who am I? Does God care about me? What's the point of all this hustling?\
\
Youth Alpha is 9 weeks of sitting with those questions together. No grades. Just honest conversation.\
\
🌟 Join us from 22 Feb
